{"tid":2499161,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【ET財智Talk】移民潮殺到　樓市響警號？（立即收看）","createTime":"2021-04-21T16:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T19:41:34.000Z","uid":24730,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c6ba06d0c375cb6e0fc5711ac90349f16522159a","tid":2499161,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T16:08:03.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">各位巴打唔信我講都信下專家講，建議睇第二段嘅詳細版，講得好中肯，睇完你會更清楚了解香港樓市而家面對乜嘢問題。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【ET財智Talk】移民潮殺到　樓市響警號？（立即收看）<br />\n 個人增值<br />\n20:00 2021/04/21<br />\n<br />\n疫情肆虐下，本港經濟遭受重大打擊，樓市看似未出現大震盪，新盤開售更見萬人空巷的情況。本港再度出現移民潮，不少中產家庭賣樓套現，會否衝擊本港樓價？有「星級地產分析員」之稱、Bricks &amp; Mortar Management主席兼總裁王震宇在《ET財智TALK》，為你分析樓市最新形勢。<br />\n<br />\nVideo Player<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wealth.hket.com/article/2937943?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2937943%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=4961c06e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2937943?r=cpsdlc</a>"},{"pid":"5b6abd2940ee6dae78a446bd69cbdd34508cf413","tid":2499161,"uid":2300,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T16:10:40.000Z","msg":"Dr MK : <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZoBFnWCvSeRfagkQZFjYcgSMenmXS9ZV1GwLS3GWgHuH?filename=cTcMhS7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTcMhS7.jpg&h=28c6ca8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b69731e3fd69d71b5e40f801246321985ae5efe0","tid":2499161,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T16:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3064810e8e472e197e40c8337a10837643eac080","tid":2499161,"uid":258903,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"cit